locality: Forest Mikea, c. 30 km north of the Manombo river. Open, scrubby, xerophytic vegetation on exposed limestone platform, near the coast, with Didiera madagascariensis and Alluaudia comosa.
5 km E of Tsiombe on road to Ambovombe.

Fiv. Fort Dauphin, Com. Ranopiso, Fkt. Andranomainty. Forêt d'Andranomainty - Antanirinaky, à 53 km W de Fort Dauphin; RN 13. Forêt sèche à Alluaudia. Récolté avec A. Ratodimanana, F. Rakotonasolo, T. Razafindrabeaza, D. Rabehevitra, Lambo et Christophe.
Mahafaly plateau, c. 39 km SW of Ampanihy, route to Androka. In scrubby, spiny vegetation on limestone escarpement with gravelly and sandy oil.
